        "text": "This slaps the piss out of every person who made a joke about that old lady who sued McDonald's over the coffee being too hot. It was too hot, it was almost boiling and they had a long list of burn complaints already. This little old lady just happened to be the kind of person they weren't afraid to crush under their foot by misleading the public - and we all bought it.\n\nA glaring look at how the media, industries, and insurance companies took an innocent woman and threw her under the bus, leaving a long legacy of government (mostly W. Bush) limiting how people can sue big business, limiting our rights and freedom in favor of big businessâ€¦"
